#
#
# (FGS)
#
# This block specifies the behavior of mouse buttons and application windows.
# In order, they permform the following:
#
#	(1) Resize window by grabbing side drag bars w/ left mouse button.
#	(2) Resize window by holding down meta key and dragging in any
#	    direction inside window with right mouse button.
#	(3) Move window by grabbing window by its title bar with left mouse
#	    button.
#	(4) Move window my holding meta key and left mouse button inside
#	    window.
#
#		
#
#
#   Mouse x [where x is 0 (any button), 1 (left), 2 (middle), 3 (right)]
# / 
# |
# |	Context: S (Sides of window)
# |		 R (Root/background window)
# |		 W (Application window)
# |		 T (Title bar)
# |		 I (Icon window)
# |		 F (Frame/corner)
# |		/
# |		|	Modifiers: N (No modifiers)
# |		|		   C (Control key)
# |		|	   /	   S (Shift key)
# |		|	  /	   M (Meta key)
# |		|	 /	   A (Any modifier)
# |		|	|
# |		|	|
# |		|	|	  Action/Function
# |		|	|	  /
# |		|	|	  |
# =====	       ===     ===     ==============================

Mouse 1		S	A	Function "Resize-or-Raise"
Mouse 1		T	A	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 1		W	M	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 1		I	A	Function "Move-or-Iconify"
Mouse 1		R	S	Desk -1 0
Mouse 1		RW	SM	Scroll -100 0 
Mouse 1		R	M	Scroll -10 0

Mouse 2		S	A	Function "Resize-or-Raise"
Mouse 2		T	A	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 2		W	M	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 2		I	A	Function "Move-or-Iconify"
#Mouse 2		I	A	Iconify

Mouse 3		S	A	Function "Resize-or-Raise"
Mouse 3		T	A	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 3		W	M	Function "Move-or-Raise"
Mouse 3		I	A	Function "Move-or-Iconify"
Mouse 3		R	S	Desk 1 0
Mouse 3		RW	SM	Scroll +100 +0 
Mouse 3		R	M	Scroll +10 +0

#Key Left	A	S 	Desk -1 0
#Key Right 	A	S	Desk 1 0

############################################################################
# Now some keyboard shortcuts.


# Arrow Keys
# press arrow + control anywhere, and scroll by 1 page
Key Left	A	SM	Scroll -100 0
Key Right	A	SM	Scroll +100 +0
Key Up		A	SM	Scroll +0   -100
Key Down	A	SM	Scroll +0   +100

# press arrow + meta key, and scroll by 1/10 of a page
Key Left	A	M	Scroll -10 +0
Key Right	A	M	Scroll +10 +0
Key Up		A	M	Scroll +0   -10
Key Down	A	M	Scroll +0   +10

# press shift arrow + control anywhere, and move the pointer by 1% of a page
Key Left	A	SC	CursorMove -1 0
Key Right	A	SC	CursorMove +1 +0
Key Up		A	SC	CursorMove +0   -1
Key Down	A	SC	CursorMove +0   +1

# press shift arrow + meta key, and move the pointer by 1/10 of a page
Key Left	A	C	CursorMove -10 +0
Key Right	A	C	CursorMove +10 +0
Key Up		A	C	CursorMove +0   -10
Key Down	A	C	CursorMove +0   +10

# Keyboard accelerators
Key F1		A	N	Popup "Utilities"
Key F2		A	N	Popup Window_Ops
Key F3		A	N	Module FvwmWinList 
Key F4		A	N	Iconify
Key F5		A	N	Move
Key F6		A	N	Resize
